tion":0},"title":"Hadith on Women: Allah reveals verses to include women","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm \u2018Umarah reported: She came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and she said, \u201cI do not see anything but for men, and I do not see anything mentioned for women.\u201d Thus, the verse was revealed, \u201cVerily, the Muslim men and women, the believing men and women,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25614,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/18\/perfume-of-men-and-women\/","url_meta":{"origin":9726,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Perfume: The perfume of men and women","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 18, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe perfume of men is that which scent is apparent and color is hidden. The perfume of women is that which scent is hidden and color is apparent.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2787 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13102,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/24\/women-gold-silk-halal\/","url_meta":{"origin":9726,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Clothing: Women can wear gold and silk, not men","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty has made lawful silk and gold for the women of my nation, but he has forbidden them for men.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 5265 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064e\u0649 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5055,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/13\/salaam-group-nisa\/","url_meta":{"origin":9726,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Greeting group of women with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Asma' bint Yazid reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by us while we were with a group of women and he greeted us with peace. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 5204 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut Imam Ibn Battal commented, \"Men greeting women and women greeting men\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31914,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/09\/hijab-women-blind-men\/","url_meta":{"origin":9726,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hijab: Women veiling themselves from men, even blind men","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: While we were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, Ibn Maktum was given permission to enter. He entered and that was after the command to veil. The Prophet said, \u201cVeil yourselves from him.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is he not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23979,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/11\/02\/treat-women-best-way\/","url_meta":{"origin":9726,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Women: Best men treat women in best manner","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best of you are the best to their women.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1978 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0648 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u062e\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064f\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.